Name: maize grain, feed to generic market for energy feed | energy feed, gross | EN15804GD, U
Category: C:Manufacturing/10:Manufacture of food products/108:Manufacture of prepared animal feeds/1080:Manufacture of prepared animal feeds
Description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/21887/documentation

This activity is a linking activity, i.e. it connects maize grain, feed with generic market for energy feed. Maize grain, feed is used primarily as a feed for animals, thus traded on generic feed market with other energy- containing products.

The activity starts with the reception of maize grain, feed.

This linking activity has the maize grain, feed as an input and protein and energy feed as outputs.
